{
  "name": "task_progress_card",
  "dsl": {
    "schema": "2.0",
    "header": {
      "title": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "任务推进阶段" },
      "template": "green"
    },
    "body": {
      "elements": [
        {
          "tag": "markdown",
          "content": "**任务推进提醒**：请跟进当前阶段任务并及时更新进度。"
        },
        {
          "tag": "column_set",
          "columns": [
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "elements": [
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**当前阶段：** {{当前阶段}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**关联需求：** {{关联需求}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**动作清单：** {{动作清单}}" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "elements": [
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**负责人：** {{负责人}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**到期时间：** {{到期时间}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**相关数据批次：** {{数据批次号}}" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "markdown",
          "content": "在任务视图中更新任务状态，完成后勾选完成标记。"
        },
        {
          "tag": "button",
          "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "打开任务视图" },
          "type": "primary",
          "behaviors": [
            {
              "type": "open_url",
              "default_url": "https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/base/DQE2bkPVba3cI5sh30ocyGh8ngh?table=tblaPTRyF17yH4Mx&view=vewnCnZg7r"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
